Package civitas.celestis.math.matrix

Class Matrix

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.grid.DoubleGrid
civitas.celestis.math.matrix.Matrix
All Implemented Interfaces:
Grid<Double>, Serializable, Iterable<Double>
public class Matrix extends DoubleGrid
A specialized DoubleGrid used in a mathematical context. Matrices provide various mathematical operations such as matrix-scalar, matrix-vector, and matrix-matrix arithmetic.
